<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.0.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <title>Criar Ambiente</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <h1>Criar Ambiente</h1>
    <p>Crie um ambiente compartilhado para sua lista de compras.</p>
    <form method="POST" action="/create-workspace" class="mt-3">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="name">Nome do ambiente</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Ex: Família Silva" required>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-success">Criar</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
